rs\", \"alia\": \"autre\", \"amiki\\u011dus\": \"se lier d\'amiti\\u00e9 avec\", \"anta\\u016dgardi\": \"circonspection, pr\\u00e9caution, avertir, d\\u00e9tourner, mettre en garde, pr\\u00e9cautionner, pr\\u00e9munir, pr\\u00e9venir\", \"apena\\u016d\": \"\\u00e0 peine\", \"atendi\": \"attendre\", \"a\\u016d\": \"ou\", \"certe\": \"certainement\", \"de\": \"de\", \"devas\": \"devoir\", \"deviga\": \"obligatoire\", \"devus\": \"devoir\", \"deziras\": \"d\\u00e9sirer\", \"diri\": \"dire\", \"diris\": \"dire\", \"eltenas\": \"supporter\", \"en\": \"dans\", \"estas\": \"\\u00eatre\", \"e\\u0109\": \"m\\u00eame, et en plus\", \"familia\": \"familial\", \"familio\": \"famille\", \"faro\": \"action\", \"feli\\u0109o\": \"bonheur, chance, veine, satisfaction\", \"fore\": \"loin, au loin\", \"forte\": \"fortement, tr\\u00e8s\", \"gardi\": \"garder\", \"granda\": \"grand(e)\", \"informi\\u011dos\": \"s\'informer, se renseigner\", \"iu\": \"quelqu\'un\", \"kaj\": \"et\", \"ke\": \"que (exemple: je sais que\\u2026, il dit que\\u2026)\", \"kelkaj\": \"quelque, un certain\", \"kia\": \"quel, quelle sorte de\", \"kiel\": \"comment, comme\", \"kiuj\": \"qui\", \"kompreneble\": \"naturellement, bien entendu\", \"kun\": \"avec\", \"kuracisto\": \"m\\u00e9decin\", \"la\": \"le, la, les\", \"longe\": \"longtemps, en long\", \"malsani\\u011di\": \"tomber malade\", \"malsanoj\": \"maladie\", \"malsanulejo\": \"h\\u00f4pital\", \"mi\": \"je\", \"mia\": \"je\", \"ne\": \"non, ne... pas\", \"necesa\": \"n\\u00e9cessaire\", \"nu\": \"allons, bien, eh bien\\u2026 \", \"oni\": \"on\", \"plezuro\": \"plaisir\", \"povos\": \"pouvoir, \\u00eatre capable de\", \"preferas\": \"pr\\u00e9f\\u00e9rer\", \"pri\": \"\\u00e0 propos de\", \"restadi\": \"s\\u00e9journer\", \"resti\": \"rester\", \"rimedo\": \"moyen, ressource, rem\\u00e8de\", \"sanon\": \"sant\\u00e9\", \"se\": \"si (indique une condition)\", \"sed\": \"mais\", \"simple\": \"simplement\", \"sin\": \"se, s\', soi\", \"tago\": \"jour\", \"tie\": \"ici, l\\u00e0\", \"tio\": \"ce, cela, \\u00e7a\", \"tuta\": \"entier, enti\\u00e8re, tout(e) le(la)/un(e)\", \"venos\": \"venir\", \"vivo\": \"vie\", \"\\u0109u\": \"est-ce que\\u2026, si (indique l\'interrogation)\", \"\\u011dis\": \"jusqu\'\\u00e0\", \"\\u015datus\": \"appr\\u00e9cier, aimer\"}}, {\"teksto\": \"Diable! Kiel rapide la tempo pasas! Jam estas preska\\u016d la kvina kaj duono. Tereza balda\\u016d alvenos, kaj mi ankora\\u016d nenion preparis. Kaj mi promesis al \\u015di pomkukon kaj mian specialan fruktosukan trinka\\u0135on. Ek, al la laboro! Mi povas pensi pri mia voja\\u011do anka\\u016d preparante la man\\u011don.\", \"vortaro\": {\"al\": \"\\u00e0, vers\", \"alvenos\": \"arriver\", \"anka\\u016d\": \"aussi\", \"ankora\\u016d\": \"encore\", \"balda\\u016d\": \"bient\\u00f4t\", \"diable\": \"diaboliquement, diablement, diable !, diantre !, fichtre !\", \"duono\": \"moiti\\u00e9\", \"ek\": \"allez !\", \"estas\": \"\\u00eatre\", \"jam\": \"d\\u00e9j\\u00e0\", \"kaj\": \"et\", \"kiel\": \"comment, comme\", \"kvina\": \"cinqui\\u00e8me\", \"la\": \"le, la, les\", \"laboro\": \"travail\", \"man\\u011don\": \"repas\", \"mi\": \"je\", \"mia\": \"je\", \"mian\": \"mon, ma\", \"nenion\": \"rien\", \"pasas\": \"passer (quelque part), s\'\\u00e9couler\", \"pensi\": \"penser\", \"povas\": \"pouvoir, \\u00eatre capable de\", \"preparante\": \"pr\\u00e9parer\", \"preparis\": \"pr\\u00e9parer\", \"preska\\u016d\": \"presque\", \"pri\": \"\\u00e0 propos de\", \"promesis\": \"promettre\", \"rapide\": \"rapidement \", \"specialan\": \"sp\\u00e9cial(e)\", \"tempo\": \"temps\", \"trinka\\u0135on\": \"boisson, breuvage\", \"voja\\u011do\": \"voyage\", \"\\u015di\": \"elle\"}}]', 1);
